  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play online with your friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Try to eliminate other players while dodging obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get power-ups with each health pack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customize your character.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/552edd6e5d1441048ffff5ef6ec0b6a7.poster.avif?t=1741784028\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/552edd6e5d1441048ffff5ef6ec0b6a7.webm?t=1741784028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/552edd6e5d1441048ffff5ef6ec0b6a7.mp4?t=1741784028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Laugh with the hilarious physics when eliminating opponents or being eliminated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/dc6f06bd3dcd2574af8446dfe121a94c.poster.avif?t=1741784028\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/dc6f06bd3dcd2574af8446dfe121a94c.webm?t=1741784028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/dc6f06bd3dcd2574af8446dfe121a94c.mp4?t=1741784028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: Gamepad doesn't work yet. You can play with it in-game (not for menus), but it might not work as expected.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note From The Developer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi everyone! I'm Darian, the creator of Crash & Bump, and I'm thrilled to introduce you to my video game. I was inspired by my love for shooter games but wanted to give it a different twist and thought that adding obstacles would be a fun way to do so, thus Crash & Bump was born. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The entire game has been made by me, and it has taken me over 3 years to develop it so far. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My goal with Crash & Bump is to offer a fun, action-packed gaming experience that puts your skills to the test. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you decide to purchase a copy, I want to thank you in advance for your support, and I hope you enjoy the game as much as I enjoy creating it. Thank you for playing Crash & Bump!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play online with your friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Try to eliminate other players while dodging obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get power-ups with each health pack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customize your character.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/552edd6e5d1441048ffff5ef6ec0b6a7.poster.avif?t=1741784028\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/552edd6e5d1441048ffff5ef6ec0b6a7.webm?t=1741784028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/552edd6e5d1441048ffff5ef6ec0b6a7.mp4?t=1741784028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Laugh with the hilarious physics when eliminating opponents or being eliminated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/dc6f06bd3dcd2574af8446dfe121a94c.poster.avif?t=1741784028\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/dc6f06bd3dcd2574af8446dfe121a94c.webm?t=1741784028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097150/extras/dc6f06bd3dcd2574af8446dfe121a94c.mp4?t=1741784028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: Gamepad doesn't work yet. You can play with it in-game (not for menus), but it might not work as expected.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note From The Developer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi everyone! I'm Darian, the creator of Crash & Bump, and I'm thrilled to introduce you to my video game. I was inspired by my love for shooter games but wanted to give it a different twist and thought that adding obstacles would be a fun way to do so, thus Crash & Bump was born. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The entire game has been made by me, and it has taken me over 3 years to develop it so far. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My goal with Crash & Bump is to offer a fun, action-packed gaming experience that puts your skills to the test. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you decide to purchase a copy, I want to thank you in advance for your support, and I hope you enjoy the game as much as I enjoy creating it. Thank you for playing Crash & Bump!</p>",
